19#include "ODEAN13Reader.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace OneD {
23
24/**
25* <p>Implements decoding of the UPC-A format.</p>
26*
27* @author dswitkin@google.com (Daniel Switkin)
28* @author Sean Owen
29*/
30class UPCAReader : public UPCEANReader
31{
32public:
33 explicit UPCAReader(const DecodeHints& hints) : UPCEANReader(hints), _reader(hints) {}
34
35 Result decodeRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row, std::unique_ptr<DecodingState>& state) const override;
36 Result decodeRow(int rowNumber, const BitArray& row, BitArray::Range startGuard) const override;
37
38protected:
39 BarcodeFormat expectedFormat() const override;
40 BitArray::Range decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin, std::string& resultString) const override;
41
42private:
43 EAN13Reader _reader;
44};

46} // OneD
47} // ZXing
